productionNode.environmentInformation:
The national eIDAS node is based on the CEF implementation. It is integrated with the central IdP Broker in Liechtenstein.
We are currently using CEF eID v2.6. eIDAS Middleware not yet integrated.

- Java OpenJDK v 11
- Apache Tomcat v 9.0.58
- No load balancer
- No proxy for outgoing connections
- Reverse proxy for incoming connections
- No HSM
